Regulation (EC) No 1182/2008 is amended as follows:
1. Article 1 is replaced by the following:
2. in Article 4, paragraphs 2 and 3 are replaced by the following:
(a) between 1 January and 15 August 2009; or
(b) between 16 August 2009 and 28 February 2010.
(a) from 16 August 2009 for the products entered into contractual storage in the period referred in paragraph 2(a);
(b) from 16 August 2010 for the products entered into contractual storage in the period referred in paragraph 2(b).
(a) on the day preceding that of the removal from storage or at the latest the last day of February following the year of entry into storage for the products entered into contractual storage in the period referred in paragraph 2(a);
(b) on the day preceding that of the removal from storage for the products entered into contractual storage in the period referred in paragraph 2(b).
(a) between 90 and 227 days for the products stored in the period referred in paragraph 2(a);
(b) maximum 365 days for the products stored in the period referred in paragraph 2(b).’;
